South African Mine Production Rose 12.4% in April, Agency Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-06-09T09:30:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-09/south-african-mine-output-increased-12-4-in-april-statistics-agency-says.html
South African mine production rose
12.4 percent in April from a year earlier, Statistics South
Africa spokesman Jean-Pierre Terblanche said by phone from
 Pretoria  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
